Add a constraint to the problem

Example:

```pycon
>>> problem = Problem()
>>> problem.addVariables(["a", "b"], [1, 2, 3])
>>> problem.addConstraint(lambda a, b: b == a+1, ["a", "b"])
>>> solutions = problem.getSolutions()
>>>
```

